public interface Expression
extends Serializable

Basic abstraction of a regular expression. All implementations of this can be converted directly into a Pattern object without risk of throwing an exception. This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients, and doing so will result in unpredictable behavior.

Method Summary

          Returns the regular expression represented by this object, in a form suitable to passing to the Pattern class.
